    "media_with_text_AryYGX": {
      "type": "media-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image_c73ehz": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/gemini-omub31li7n.jpg",
            "media_width": 50,
            "media_position": "start",
            "text_position": "place-self-center text-center",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<h3><strong>A deliberate choice.</strong></h3><p>I wanted quality. But above all, I wanted every woman to be able to afford it. I looked in France, in Belgium, across Europe. But producing in Europe would have made VELVY out of reach for most of you. So I travelled back and forth to China with our sketches, our prototypes, our standards. We didn't look for the fastest. Or the cheapest. We looked for those capable of delivering exactly what we had imagined. Because manufacturing abroad doesn't mean manufacturing carelessly.</p><h3><strong>10,000 women later.</strong></h3><p>Today, over 10,000 women wear VELVY. And what moves me most are your messages.</p><p><em>\"I could never go back to regular clips.\"</em></p><p>From the very beginning, I read every piece of feedback, every comment, every experience. Because that's exactly how you build a real product — by listening to the women who wear it every day. It's thanks to you that VELVY keeps getting better.</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
